            <div type="section" xml:id="Legislation">
                <head>Legislation</head>
                <p>Legislation stipulates that public records come available after 20 years.
                    However, diplomatic records may remain classified for 75 years. </p>
            </div>
            <div type="section" xml:id="Location">
                <head>Location</head>
                <p>Ministry of Foreign Affairs: "Dame Gruev" St. No. 6, 1 000 Skopje.</p>
                <p>State Archives: Grigor Prilchev No. 3, 1000 Skopje. </p>
            </div>
            <div type="section" xml:id="Procedures">
                <head>Procedures</head>
                <p>Researchers should contact the State Archives to inquire about access to relevant
                    diplomatic records. </p>
            </div>
